articles.title: Fewer Americans sought unemployment benefits last week as job cuts stay low - AP News
articles.description: The number of Americans applying for unemployment benefits declined last week in a sign that layoffs remain low, even as several high-profile companies have announced job cuts. U.S. applications for unemployment benefits in the week ending Nov. 22 dropped 6,0…
